receiver_country¶

The receiver country refers to the country targeted by the cyber incident.

The following receiver countries can be queried in the database, use the ISO alpha-3 country codes. Leaving the filter to its default value (None) will return all receiver countries.

  • AFG - Afghanistan

  • ALB - Albania

  • DZA - Algeria

  • ASM - American Samoa

  • AND - Andorra

  • AGO - Angola

  • AIA - Anguilla
